For very first time:

Install Heroku for your system

$ sudo npm install -g heroku   (For Ububtu)
$ heroku login or $ heroku login -i
$ heroku keys:add
$ heroku keys
$ heroku keys:remove your_email_id (if you want to remove any key)
$ ssh -v git@heroku.com
$ env
After this check your git status and push local changes to your git repo to push it to live server.
$ heroku create
$ git push heroku
$ heroku addons:create mongolab:sandbox  (For using addons)
$ heroku config
$ heroku open


Next times:

Check your git status and push local changes to your git repo to push it to live server.
$ git push heroku
$ heroku open
